	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you want to take a group and hunt in Skyshrine around the pool room, the Guardian armor is excellent and looks slick with Velious or Luclin graphics on.&nbsp;&nbsp;It's also pretty good experience at your level.  And if you ever upgrade you'll want to keep the Guardian stuff for your resist kit, since a few pieces are exceptionally good and free is very cheap. :)<br><br>For non-visible pieces I would suggest:<br><br>Shoulders - Tattered Mantle<br><br>Fingers - Velium Fire Opal rings (you'll be wearing these at 60), or if that's too expensive Jagged Bands<br><br>Ears - Electrum Black Sapphire Earrings (you'll be wearing these at 60)<br><br>Belt - Flowing Black Silk Sash (Centi Warspear = awesome)<br><br>Neck - Ry`Gorr Collar<br><br>And all the Deepwater you can buy.  That is all!<br>&nbsp;<br><b>Praetor</b>, 60th Crusader<br>Avatars of Discord</td></tr>
